author: Giorgio Mendoza
description: The HH-SCDAYU800A is another RISC-V development board built around the Alibaba T-Head TH1520 system-on-chip. With its dual Gigabit Ethernet ports, multiple camera interfaces, and industrial-grade design, the board targets applications requiring multimedia features, edge inference, and smart device integration. title: RISC-V Embedded Board Features TH1520 SoC, Dual GbE, and 4TOPS AI
